{"ConnectionString":"","SqlQuery":"INSERT dbo.Asaei_EHaml_ReplyToInquiry
 ( InquiryId ,
 InquiryType ,
 ServentUserId ,
 KoleModatZamaneHaml ,
 ZamaneAmadegiBarayShoorooeAmaliyatShamsi ,
 ZamaneAmadegiBarayShoorooAmaliyatMiladi ,
 GozaresheAmaliyateRoozane ,
 PishbiniEmkanPaziriyeAmaliyat ,
 GeymateKol ,
 Vaziyat ,

 CreateDateMiladi
 ) Output Inserted.Id
VALUES ( [Get:InquiryId] , -- InquiryId - bigint
 N'[InquiryType]' , -- InquiryType - nvarchar(1000)

 N'[ZamaneAmadegiBarayeShoorooeAmaliyat]' , -- ZamaneAmadegiBarayShoorooeAmaliyatShamsi - nvarchar(1000)
 dbo.PersianToGregorian(CONVERT(VARCHAR, '[ZamaneAmadegiBarayeShoorooeAmaliyat]', 120)) , -- ZamaneAmadegiBarayShoorooAmaliyatMiladi - date
 N'خیر' , -- GozaresheAmaliyateRoozane - nvarchar(1000)
 N'[PishbiniEmkanPaziriyeAmaliyat]' , -- PishbiniEmkanPaziriyeAmaliyat - nvarchar(1000)
 N'[GeymateKol]' , -- GeymateKol - nvarchar(1000)
 N'در حال بررسی' , -- Vaziyat - nvarchar(1000)
 dbo.GregorianToPersian(CONVERT(VARCHAR, GETDATE(), 120)) , -- CreateDateShamsi - nvarchar(1000)
 GETDATE() -- CreateDateMiladi - date
 )","OutputTokenName":"OutputedReplyToInquiryId","ExtractColumns":"","ShowErrors":""}
